---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pricing â€” Hanzo Bot" description="Simple, transparent pricing. Run locally for free or deploy to the cloud starting at $5/mo.">
  <div class="stars"></div>
  <div class="nebula"></div>

  <main class="container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">Simple, Transparent Pricing</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        Run locally for free. Deploy to the cloud when you need always-on agents.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <!-- Free / Local -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="pricing-badge">Free Forever</div>
        <h2 class="pricing-name">Local</h2>
        <div class="pricing-amount">
          <span class="pricing-dollar">$</span>
          <span class="pricing-value">0</span>
        </div>
        <p class="pricing-period">Run on your own machine</p>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>macOS, Windows, or Linux</li>
          <li>Bring your own API keys (OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.)</li>
          <li>All 600+ integrations</li>
          <li>All messaging channels</li>
          <li>Full system access (files, terminal, browser)</li>
          <li>Persistent memory & context</li>
          <li>Skills & plugins</li>
          <li>Open source</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/#quickstart" class="pricing-cta pricing-cta-secondary">Download Now</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Cloud Linux -->
      <div class="pricing-card pricing-card-featured">
        <div class="pricing-badge pricing-badge-hot">Most Popular</div>
        <h2 class="pricing-name">Cloud Linux</h2>
        <div class="pricing-amount">
          <span class="pricing-dollar">$</span>
          <span class="pricing-value">5</span>
          <span class="pricing-unit">/mo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="pricing-period">per bot instance</p>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>Full Linux VM with desktop environment</li>
          <li>100+ AI models included (no API keys needed)</li>
          <li>Browser & full computer use</li>
          <li>Always-on, 24/7 uptime</li>
          <li>All messaging channels connected</li>
          <li>Hanzo Cloud dashboard</li>
          <li>Automatic updates</li>
          <li>1 GB persistent storage</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://app.hanzo.bot" class="pricing-cta pricing-cta-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Start Free Trial</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Cloud Mac/Win -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="pricing-badge">Pro</div>
        <h2 class="pricing-name">Cloud Mac / Windows</h2>
        <div class="pricing-amount">
          <span class="pricing-dollar">$</span>
          <span class="pricing-value">25</span>
          <span class="pricing-unit">/mo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="pricing-period">per bot instance</p>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li>Full macOS or Windows VM</li>
          <li>Native app automation (Xcode, Office, etc.)</li>
          <li>100+ AI models included</li>
          <li>Priority support</li>
          <li>Custom model fine-tuning</li>
          <li>Team management & SSO</li>
          <li>10 GB persistent storage</li>
          <li>SLA guarantee</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://app.hanzo.bot" class="pricing-cta pricing-cta-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Contact Sales</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Enterprise -->
    <div class="enterprise-card">
      <div class="enterprise-inner">
        <div class="enterprise-text">
          <h3 class="enterprise-title">Enterprise</h3>
          <p class="enterprise-desc">
            Self-hosted deployment, custom models, dedicated infrastructure, compliance certifications, and white-glove onboarding. Let's talk.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="mailto:sales@hanzo.ai" class="pricing-cta pricing-cta-secondary">Contact Sales</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="faq">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="accent-mark">&#x27E9;</span> Frequently Asked
      </h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="faq-q">What's included in the free tier?</h3>
          <p class="faq-a">Everything. You get the full Hanzo Bot running on your machine with all integrations, all channels, and all skills. The only thing you provide is your own AI model API keys.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="faq-q">What does "full VM" mean?</h3>
          <p class="faq-a">Each cloud bot instance gets its own virtual machine with a real desktop environment. It can browse the web, run apps, write code, manage files, and do everything a human team member can do on a computer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="faq-q">Can I use my own API keys in the cloud?</h3>
          <p class="faq-a">Yes. Cloud plans include access to 100+ models via Hanzo LLM Gateway, but you can also bring your own OpenAI, Anthropic, or any other provider keys.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="faq-q">Why is Mac/Windows more expensive?</h3>
          <p class="faq-a">macOS and Windows VMs require licensed hardware and specialized infrastructure. Linux VMs are much cheaper to provision, which is why we can offer them at $5/mo.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="faq-q">Is there a free trial?</h3>
          <p class="faq-a">Yes. Cloud plans come with a 14-day free trial. No credit card required. You can also run locally for free forever.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3 class="faq-q">Can I run multiple bots?</h3>
          <p class="faq-a">Absolutely. Each bot instance is independent with its own memory, channels, and configuration. Run as many as you need for different roles or teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="primary-cta">
      <a href="https://app.hanzo.bot" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg class="btn-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M15 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-4"/>
          <polyline points="10 17 15 12 10 7"/>
          <line x1="15" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/>
        </svg>
        Get Started Free
      </a>
      <p class="primary-cta-note">No credit card required. Deploy your AI team in minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .stars {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 20px 30px, rgba(255,255,255,0.8), transparent),
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 40px 70px, rgba(255,255,255,0.5), transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 90px 40px, rgba(255,255,255,0.6), transparent),
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 130px 80px, rgba(255,255,255,0.4), transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 160px 120px, rgba(255,255,255,0.7), transparent);
    background-size: 350px 200px;
    animation: twinkle 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  @keyframes twinkle {
    0% { opacity: 0.4; }
    100% { opacity: 0.7; }
  }

  .nebula {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 20% 20%, rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.12), transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 80% 30%, rgba(0, 229, 204, 0.08), transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px 40px;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text-primary) 0%, var(--coral-bright) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.1s both;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .pricing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .pricing-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    background: rgba(10, 15, 26, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .pricing-card-featured {
    border-color: var(--coral-bright);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.06) 0%, rgba(10, 15, 26, 0.8) 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.08);
  }

  .pricing-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .pricing-badge-hot {
    color: var(--coral-bright);
  }

  .pricing-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .pricing-amount {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .pricing-dollar {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .pricing-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .pricing-unit {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-left: 2px;
  }

  .pricing-period {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .pricing-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .pricing-features li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding-left: 22px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .pricing-features li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 6px;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--cyan-bright);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .pricing-card-featured .pricing-features li::before {
    background: var(--coral-bright);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .pricing-cta {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .pricing-cta-primary {
    color: #050810;
    background: var(--coral-bright);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.3);
  }

  .pricing-cta-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.4);
    background: #ff6b6b;
  }

  .pricing-cta-secondary {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  }

  .pricing-cta-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--coral-bright);
    background: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.06);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Enterprise */
  .enterprise-card {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  .enterprise-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    background: rgba(10, 15, 26, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .enterprise-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  .enterprise-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .enterprise-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.3s both;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .accent-mark {
    color: var(--coral-bright);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .faq-item {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    background: rgba(10, 15, 26, 0.6);
  }

  .faq-q {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .faq-a {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Primary CTA */
  .primary-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.4s both;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #050810;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fd4444 0%, #e03e3e 100%);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.45);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #fd4444 100%);
  }

  .btn-icon {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
  }

  .primary-cta-note {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
</style>
